description:
This is a 19 minute workout called 'Drop Your Split Row: #9 of 11' from the channel Laine Karwoski.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Competitor vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record..
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Welcome to workout 9 in the Drop Your Split series with Laine. This 18-minute Drive is the closest simulation to your ultimate 20-minute test, starting five splits above your goal average and gradually lowering throughout. Embrace the challenge, stay focused, and prepare for your best performance! Max rhythm: 30, Format: Endurance....
